virtual AKRESULT AK::IAkPluginParam::Term ( IAkPluginMemAlloc *  in_pAllocator  )  [pure virtual]

Called by the sound engine when a parameter node is terminated.

Note: The self-destruction of the parameter node must be done using the AK_PLUGIN_DELETE() macro.
Returns:
AK_Success if successful, AK_Fail otherwise
